      EQUIPT:  SHADOWED TOOLING


      Tools, never enough! The Rotorway uses certain tools frequently and they need to be readily available. I created this cart to serve specifically the 162F. Everytime I discover the need for a unique tool it gets added to the collection.









      All tools are "shadowed" into the cart. At the end of the maintenance day it is simple to perform a tool inventory which insures that no tool is left on the aircraft.









      ​

      The tools currently in the cart are tools that have been required to this point in my re-build. There is room for growth. The cart was purchased from Harbor Freight.











      I tried to organize the drawers based on frequency of use. Many tools are duplicates of tools within my shop.











      This rollaway has saved me many trips to the shop! The lid also provides a flat surface to lay things on while working.
